+CLASS="REFSECT1"
+><A
+NAME="AEN1068"
+></A
+><H2
+>HISTORY</H2
+><P
+>The <B
+CLASS="COMMAND"
+>tftpd</B
+> command appeared in 4.2BSD. The source in iputils
+is cleaned up both syntactically (ANSIized) and semantically (UDP socket IO).</P
+><P
