+the description from there.
+.SH "SEE ALSO"
+.PP
+\fBtraceroute\fR(8),
+\fBtracepath\fR(8),
+\fBping\fR(8).
+.SH "HISTORY"
+.PP
+This program has long history. Author of \fBtraceroute\fR
